{
    "tagId": "2"
}

### Update file

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/files/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Delete file

DELETE  {{baseUrl}}/files/3 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{token}}




